{"id": "1228312309080916069", "channel_id": "1228312309080916069", "type": 0, "author_id": "190674373483429888", "author_name": ".weiyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "**文前省流**：個人對達芙的評價，為高難環境乏力、日常摸魚親民，\n存在極限操作空間，但跟簡單強大、數值暴力等詞彙不沾邊的限定喚醒體\n\n此外，本文撰寫於癲三滿分時代，在癲五版本上線後，\n許多內容已不再具有實操參考性，\n僅能幫助各位建立一些關於達芙戴爾的基礎觀念\n\n\nID：100292185 ，目前常掛小玫瑰奧爾拉，\n本體+4超限帶專武+極夜，單卡解決死抗需求\n\n-------------------------------------------------------\n## 【目錄跳轉】\n- 前言\n- [體質&技能介紹](https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1228312309080916069/1228312416148783177)\n- [日常用法](https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1228312309080916069/1228313224202551397)\n- [結語](https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1228312309080916069/1228313496303964191)\n- [進階打法(癲三滿分配置)](https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1228312309080916069/1236283169955909714)\n-------------------------------------------------------\n## 【前言】\n\n```百年四月薰風驅散她的芬芳，\n千年十月淫雨沖刷她的足跡，\n無情歲月侵襲她存在的舊憶，然而\näŒåŸ·æµ·æ所行之處，\n山川永世存憶。```\n\n達芙戴爾，別稱大福袋、紫夫人、阿姨、牢芙\n她是超維界域中第一名登場的限定喚醒體\n也是問世沒多久，就促成環境超維折疊的始作俑者\n\n平衡修正後的大福袋，傷害能力相較以前被大幅限制，\n無法再依靠不斷的疊加『斷頸一擊』直接通關副本，\n面對如今高難Boss過長的血條時，\n甚至有可能需要其他輸出位的幫助\n\n如今她的口碑似乎並不算好，\n不僅在超維榜的使用率堪憂，\n討論起強度更是限定倒數的有力競爭者，\n但其實，平衡調整並沒有帶走達芙的所有特色，\n反而在功能性方面還獲得了一些補償\n\n思索再三，最後我還是沒有選擇退回，\n留下了這位剛入坑時第一個抽的限定，\n無論是還在堅持的使用者也好，\n已經退回、好奇達芙目前狀況的守密人也罷，\n下面，是一些關於當前版本達芙戴爾的使用Tips\n\n下面主要向新手入門、還沒怎麼玩過大福袋的玩家", "timestamp": "2024-04-12T11:54:35.424000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-07-19T02:39:39.917000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 36}, {"emoji": "🍆", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "👌", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "🙏", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1228312309080916069", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "重返絕叫哀號的原質之海（新版達芙，從入門到入土）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179680056791130", "1174179755759763526"]}
{"id": "1228143882449977394", "channel_id": "1228143882449977394", "type": 0, "author_id": "485414453152841749", "author_name": "wodebaobaoxiaodangaovi", "author_bot": false, "content": "擴展陣容比提升強度重要強度（限角多抽那怕0啟😉）\n通關順序同樣是54321\n血肉輔助全界域最強，輸出角色足夠可以出3隊\n0啟旺達直接把4-3尤烏按在地上扁\n\n凹凹凹凹凹凹凹凹凹凹凹凹凹凹凹", "timestamp": "2024-04-12T00:45:19.386000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "879768899711823922", "emoji_id": "1069262194497290260", "count": 2}, {"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1228143883318329444", "filename": "IMG_1139.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2218653, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228143882449977394/1228143883318329444/IMG_1139.png?ex=69fb37df&is=69f9e65f&hm=18cdb0d39752beacb55170a7a14c3473bede023a17b3893c26ffb7badb4e10c2&"}, {"id": "1228143883985092679", "filename": "IMG_1140.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2216077, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228143882449977394/1228143883985092679/IMG_1140.png?ex=69fb37df&is=69f9e65f&hm=55406c87336bf57e7645d49b21c006461f2531eac437e82633f54bc347bda058&"}, {"id": "1228143884652122154", "filename": "IMG_1145.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1641569, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228143882449977394/1228143884652122154/IMG_1145.png?ex=69fb37df&is=69f9e65f&hm=4cbb5cbdea3cb3587f6e550ec083620b4aea4be86f14f39c59603785edb8a5f5&"}, {"id": "1228143885276938385", "filename": "IMG_1144.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1663406, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228143882449977394/1228143885276938385/IMG_1144.png?ex=69fb37e0&is=69f9e660&hm=e5ce3bb52b19ef48be6afa5fddacbbb2de87cd812311f1fb713f8261dad586d8&"}, {"id": "1228143885994299402", "filename": "IMG_1143.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1683157, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228143882449977394/1228143885994299402/IMG_1143.png?ex=69fb37e0&is=69f9e660&hm=f4a556c555adc284f535376f9574cd26bcba3fabda4e912059739ae0f45c9b28&"}, {"id": "1228143886526971914", "filename": "IMG_1142.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1648104, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228143882449977394/1228143886526971914/IMG_1142.png?ex=69fb37e0&is=69f9e660&hm=30e474b3d8786264241b6f507f62dccfb5ddfb5823aade85ab6dc0e8f850b0ab&"}, {"id": "1228143887386808320", "filename": "IMG_1141.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1677366, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228143882449977394/1228143887386808320/IMG_1141.png?ex=69fb37e0&is=69f9e660&hm=898162d775086a65562086c65454636ca0fa88867780be04b53f2a22f6a1a72f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1228143882449977394", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融災350分享", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748", "1174179755759763526"]}
{"id": "1228397723389263882", "channel_id": "1228397723389263882", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "鑒於神父活動已開放掉落最高的最後一關，因此簡單用了個EXCEL表格計算對照45等金卷本的收益，弄完順手發上來給各位參考。\n\n  使用方法：可於紅色數字處，輸入個人額外掉落率，50%輸入0.5，150%輸入1.5。或直接參考下方各掉落率的收益對照。刷的關卡不同，掉落數量不同也能自行調整。\n  單次商店除特殊物品外的總收益換算為523000金卷+500調查徽章+50銀芯，可對照「同等體力刷金卷本收益」進行對比。\n\n  內容介紹：商店價值換算以當前金卷商店的價格為主，而三個商店總價值是相等的。\n\n  依照本次個人掉落紀錄，期望值估計為：基礎掉落50%，10/9倍 30%，11/9倍 20%。\n\np.s.收益期望為個人掉落數據結果推估的預期，可能有所偏差，謹慎參考。excel下方同時附上本次掉落數據。\n\n僅供參考，有問題請指正。", "timestamp": "2024-04-12T17:33:59.782000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-04-16T07:41:23.510000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [{"id": "1228397723510902806", "filename": "cb9556d87cfe38d3.xlsx", "content_type": "application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet", "size": 13336, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228397723389263882/1228397723510902806/cb9556d87cfe38d3.xlsx?ex=69fb7b87&is=69fa2a07&hm=2d276d035150afae6ea9a4ff03e61d2d299eec8581536466d4b2dd82b61ee9cc&"}, {"id": "1228397723993116805", "filename": "b48b6324efbef449.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 93145, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228397723389263882/1228397723993116805/b48b6324efbef449.JPG?ex=69fb7b87&is=69fa2a07&hm=1a15a607572589c72cd5ce0e5cdda37013f7a7392ff02b21b615e44f6a5ca0b2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1228397723389263882", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "神父活動收益", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1228409639759253524", "channel_id": "1228409639759253524", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "▶特遣記錄的關卡已經優化到只剩下一張了。\n▶经过毒地板（紫色格子）时，会扣除 血量上限 的约5%，也就是固定值。当踏入毒地板所扣除的血量被判断为致命伤害，则触发死亡抵抗/复活确认。\np.s.最後一張地圖「懺悔」和特遣記錄的這張地圖不一樣，有微改。改動就是在最下面把救贖和黑印圖標換了一下，就只是這樣。~~你們甚至不捨得重新做一張地圖，只是換了地板皮膚和格子圖標互換。~~\nuid100001547", "timestamp": "2024-04-12T18:21:20.866000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-04-12T18:24:36.087000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1228409639960445020", "filename": "Image_1712945293699.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 134267, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228409639759253524/1228409639960445020/Image_1712945293699.jpg?ex=69fb86a0&is=69fa3520&hm=8ad7f20768ead1d118478ec39005cd661eba40dce76811860f0b7ccabdcca01b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1228409639759253524", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "特遣記錄「血的顏色」地圖總覽", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1228408943165050921", "channel_id": "1228408943165050921", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "▶限時活動「聖堂之路」入口，在主介面左下角「福利」-「靈魂的牧人」處進入。\n▶每個關卡的敵人與事件都可能發生隨機變化。\n▶經過毒地板（紫色格子）時，會扣除 血量上限 的約5%，也就是固定值。當踏入毒地板所扣除的血量被判斷爲致命傷害，則觸發死亡抵抗/復活確認。\np.s.最後一張地圖「懺悔」和特遣記錄的那張地圖不一樣，有微改。改動就是在最下面把救贖和黑印圖標換了一下，就只是這樣。\nuid100001547", "timestamp": "2024-04-12T18:18:34.785000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-04-12T18:24:07.051000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1228408943567700007", "filename": "Image_1712945290150.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 327561, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228408943165050921/1228408943567700007/Image_1712945290150.jpg?ex=69fb85fa&is=69fa347a&hm=3703f2e3b0fd53dcc09a8093b2e3d0aba79cc232a007d0c06a4fc81d99afb786&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1228408943165050921", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "「圣堂之路」地图总览", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1228163815372361859", "channel_id": "1228163815372361859", "type": 0, "author_id": "1223503015852380160", "author_name": "squire5771", "author_bot": false, "content": "这里是女王之剑，一个拉蒙娜厨，自从深潜改成死抗模式打融灾似乎也得心应手了，由于楼主阵容比较偏，这是一期参考性比较低的350攻略。本期灵摆比较上期比较烂但好在后三波boss都比较好打。因为我的希莉练度不够选择打3-1，觉醒希洛，带埋骨雷亚成长更多力量，死抗扛住第七回合动手就行，3-2的钥令给灵感适合深海算力大户，带图墨不死鸟水母，带谵妄可以节省觉醒资源，觉醒顺序墨菲希莱水母，道中多开静海稳住血量，boss第七回合图墨水母一波狂气就带走了，3-3选择血肉盾击，注意到地图右边有一个复制卡牌的事件，先走左边商店刷镜像刻印给心眼利刃，然后再复制就有四张利刃了，卡删高热和回旋，道中神父清杂，boss本来想把盾叠超过上限的，但是我神父没二启算力不够，实际熔炉还是回血为主，有胚胎对轴很方便，神父吞噬艾尔瓦开大盾击便是。3-4莉兹打尤乌很有优势，因为尤乌会在被毒后才狂暴，控制住他就很简单，地图有非常多幻象，带活性可以很好得净化牌库，我拿到了沉重画框，这让三张带有虚弱易伤的指令卡都有较高收益，boss流血那波朵尔大招顶一下，宁妃爆毒正好可以让boss进二阶段，觉醒奥吉尔莉兹。3-5是我常用的一套超维潘，普通环境通常是拉蒙娜双大检索两次鞭子让潘打出超高爆发，但是融灾环境要放弃这种想法，前几波拉蒙娜该开大就开，因为没有治疗落地战要凹，保证落地战结束还剩半血，商店镜像了鞭子，打精英我拿了一个意识铭刻，对轴方便，而且这样触发死抗也不会浪费摸牌，事件给的差分机很强，配合拉蒙娜觉醒或者灵感可以把算力变成三再打鞭子。这套埋骨温柯尔非常重要，没有充能潘boss战开不出三次大招（前两次大招会打出锁血）。造物拿一些力量双暴算力相关就好。以上就是本期攻略全部内容，祝大家深潜195融灾350，主线全成就，活动一命过。\nuid:100303407", "timestamp": "2024-04-12T02:04:31.765000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-04-12T02:04:49.971000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1228163815686930452", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-04-12-09-14-33-995_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 234641, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228163815372361859/1228163815686930452/Screenshot_2024-04-12-09-14-33-995_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb4a6f&is=69f9f8ef&hm=cf8d6a5b7ee0b885897fcd17dc8e8e9127f1d28168e7b50e2893c8e41dd5c098&"}, {"id": "1228163816068481127", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-04-12-09-14-40-867_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 266051, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228163815372361859/1228163816068481127/Screenshot_2024-04-12-09-14-40-867_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb4a6f&is=69f9f8ef&hm=03c61be8c9c7874b3cea03fa167191b8114b653d2a25cc083d8379fc81383a9e&"}, {"id": "1228163816420937738", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-04-12-09-14-46-396_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 284276, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228163815372361859/1228163816420937738/Screenshot_2024-04-12-09-14-46-396_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb4a70&is=69f9f8f0&hm=58a0f222317f7b802d2afbecabf88848ebf1253beee3a0b2774a3aa61d158e99&"}, {"id": "1228163816785838290", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-04-12-09-14-51-618_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 271453, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228163815372361859/1228163816785838290/Screenshot_2024-04-12-09-14-51-618_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb4a70&is=69f9f8f0&hm=f7e2d37cfc57aababecc0c46d6ae21d8c0be211679c5438406f30d68f101598e&"}, {"id": "1228163817058598952", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-04-12-09-15-00-653_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 273305, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228163815372361859/1228163817058598952/Screenshot_2024-04-12-09-15-00-653_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb4a70&is=69f9f8f0&hm=2f1c4d81744504b96594bcedf49ed5a2036b0dfe042f4eaa7543c3e737b61d9c&"}, {"id": "1228163817373044746", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-04-12-09-15-05-920_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 267715, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228163815372361859/1228163817373044746/Screenshot_2024-04-12-09-15-05-920_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb4a70&is=69f9f8f0&hm=822e293b0981086e23891e886529f7970d3c2fff1c46025508d676ae069b91ad&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1228163815372361859", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融灾350攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1181143392739147778"]}
